Text: Vishak is very adaptable to fast-paced startup product development. He did really well on researching and providing data insights on our product development team. His data analysis guided us to make important decisions throughout the product discovery process. I recommended working with Vishak!

Vishak is a hard working and extremely curious analyst who will generate ideas and answers quickly with little direction. He’s a self starter and one of the brightest minds I’ve had the fortune of working with. I know he has a great future ahead in this field.
